					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13875647#post-4827364</guid>
				<title>(no title)</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13875647/scp-5702#post-4827364</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Wed, 25 Nov 2020 01:41:14 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>LordStonefish</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2527320</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is my homage to all the great testing log articles on site I still love to read and adore, as well as cinephilia. Sort of the bastard child of <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-1756">At The Movies</a> and <a href="http://www.scpwiki.com/scp-3977">Hawaiian Punch</a>.</p> <p>Specials thanks to pastarasta1 and Uncle Nicolini for critique, and to pastarasta1 for the beautiful logo, which comes from <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/144397451@N07/30961017405">https://www.flickr.com/photos/144397451@N07/30961017405</a>.</p> <p>Additionally, in the testing log, note that any moving picture can be generated. Animation, pornographic films, web content, advertisements, so long as it fits the Wikipedia sentence template.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
